 <span data-ttu-id="a26ee-285">В следующем примере демонстрируются <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> свойства <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> и класса.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a26ee-285">The following example demonstrates the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Username%2A> and <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Password%2A> properties of the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> class.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a26ee-286">В этом примере получается указанный <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> пользователем <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A> и все его <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>свойства.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a26ee-286">This example gets the user-specified <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> and the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A> of all its <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Children%2A>.</span></span>  
  
